# AI Creative Infrastructure

Unified, enterprise‑ready architecture for adaptive, sovereign, multi‑modal creation.

This repository contains public documentation only. Sensitive evidence, raw logs, and legal artifacts are maintained in private, access‑controlled archives and are not included here.

## Overview
- Identity and authorship governance
- Multi‑agent cognition and orchestration
- Multi‑modal creative engines (audio, narrative, technical)
- Workflow automation and provenance controls
- Enterprise integration patterns

## Architecture
Identity Layer
  ├─ Cognition Layer (multi‑agent)
  ├─ Creative Engines (audio, narrative, technical)
  ├─ Orchestration Layer (workflow)
  ├─ Verification Layer (provenance)
  └─ Deployment Layer (public artifacts)

## Evidence and Provenance
A separate, timestamped evidence corpus is preserved off‑platform for legal and partnership needs. This repository references that corpus but does not contain it.

## Roadmap
Phase 1 Documentation and Governance
Phase 2 Platform Integrations
Phase 3 Enterprise Rollout

